    "Moreover, the authors give a heuristic for the case when the proportion of customers of each type is random and provide empirical evidence of the applicability of their approach.",
    "Moreover, Martínez-de Albéniz and Kunnumkal (2022) consider the joint assortment and inventory planning problem under stockout-based substitution in a setting with inventory replenishment.",
